2 8 14 3 2 Special Abilities: Wookies begin the game with one rank in Brawl.  They still may not train Brawl above rank 2 during character creation.

Wookie Rage: When a Wookie has suffered any wounds, he deals +1 damage to Brawl and Melee attacks.  When a Wookie is Critically Injured, he instead deals +2 damage to Brawl and Melee attacks.
